text: Kubagushevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mindyaksky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 377 as of 2010. There are 12 streets. == Geography == It is located 81 km from Uchaly, 16 km from Mindyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kubagushevo
